# ===========================================
# KEEP ONLY THESE ESSENTIAL FILES/FOLDERS:
# ===========================================
# 
# Core Application:
# - app.R (main application file)
# - modules/ (application modules)
# - www/ (web assets if any, excluding duplicate docs)
# 
# Documentation:
# - README.md
# - LICENSE  
# - CONTRIBUTING.md
# - CHANGELOG.md
# - INSTALL.md
# - GITHUB_CHECKLIST.md
# - docs/ (user and developer documentation)
# 
# Data & Configuration:
# - example_data/ (sample datasets)
# - .github/ (GitHub templates and workflows)
# - .gitignore
# - APP.Rproj
# 
# App Resources:
# - inst/ (contains QC report template)
# - framework_roadmap.md (development roadmap)
# ===========================================
